description:
An all-new eight-issue series composed of four 48-page stories!

These brand new exploitation stories are written by Alex de Campi and illustrated by four different artists and contain strong sexual content and graphic violence. Continued from Grindhouse: Doors Open At Midnight.

Slay Ride - A dark Christmas tale about things that you believe in and that you fear... and what happens when they come to life. Slay Ride is not a story of too many words but of a lot of blood and leaves everything else to the reader's imagination.

Blood Lagoon (sequel to Bee Vixens From Mars) - second story line.

Lady Danger: Agent of B.O.O.T.I. (Bureau of Organized Terrorism Intervention) - third.

Nebulina - fourth.

Collected Editions

  • Grindhouse: Doors Open At Midnight Double Feature - Slay Ride/Blood Lagoon (#1-4)
